<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.5.1">
<l>tantaikā lilvilaṅ kaṟavantu tōṉṟiya tōṉṟalpiṉ tamiyēṉṟaṉ</l>
<l>cintai pōyiṟṟut tiruvaruḷ avaṉiṭaip peṟumaḷa viruntēṉai</l>
<l>anti kāvala ṉamutuṟu pacuṅkati ravaicuṭa vataṉōṭum</l>
<l>manta mārutam vaṉamulai taṭavantu valiceyva toḻiyātē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I was [left] alone; my mind went after the vision who appeared,</l>
<l rend="indent">coming to cut the fetters from his father’s feet.</l>
<l>[Now] along with when the night-watchman’s ambrosia-filled,</l>
<l rend="indent">cool rays burn,</l>
<l>The soft breeze coming on the breadth of my beautiful breasts,</l>
<l>[The] inflicting of pain upon me who waits</l>
<l rend="indent">until gaining divine grace from him, does not stop.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
